# Infrastructure & deploy

## Local

```bash
pnpm db:up    # infrastructure/docker/docker-compose.yml → Postgres :5435, Redis :6381
pnpm db:down
```

## Production stack

| File | Role |
|------|------|
| `backend/Dockerfile` | API image (monorepo root context) |
| `infrastructure/docker/docker-compose.prod.yml` | API + Postgres + Redis + Caddy |
| `infrastructure/docker/Caddyfile` | `:80` → api:3001 |
| `backend/.env.production.example` | Env template |

## Hetzner deploy

```bash
export HCLOUD_TOKEN='...'
./infrastructure/hetzner/up.sh
```

Requires: verified Hetzner account, project `payspin`, SSH key `~/.ssh/id_ed25519_payspin`.

Deploy streams Docker image over SSH — Hub push optional (`infrastructure/docker/publish.sh`).

## Security

- Postgres/Redis on internal Docker network only
- Firewall: 22, 80, 443 on VPS
- Secrets on server at `/opt/payspin/.env.production` — never commit

## Account

Hetzner + Docker Hub: **payspin.app@gmail.com** only.
